Class FibonacciNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • FibonacciNode

  • public class FibonacciNode
extends java.lang.Object
    FibonacciNode object is used to store data in Fibonacci heap

      Constructor and Description
      FibonacciNode()
      Creates a Fibonacci heap node with hashKey=null.
